paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.graphx._

case class Paper(id: Long, year: Int, title: String, authors: String)

val papers = sc.textFile("/zeppelin/data/cit-HepTh-papers.txt").map(line => line.split("\t")).map(parts => Paper(parts(0).toLong, parts(1).toInt, parts(2), parts(3)))
val citations = sc.textFile("/zeppelin/data/cit-HepTh.txt").map(line => line.split("\t")).map(parts => (parts(0).toLong, parts(1).toLong))

val vertices = papers.map(paper => (paper.id, paper))
val edges = citations.map(c => Edge(c._1, c._2, "cited"))

val graph = Graph(vertices, edges).cache

paragraphs.text:
case class IdDegree(id: Long, degree: Int)

val inDegrees = graph.inDegrees.map({ case (id, degree) => IdDegree(id, degree)}).toDF.cache

inDegrees.registerTempTable("inDegrees")

result.msg:
defined class IdDegree
inDegrees: org.apache.spark.sql.DataFrame = [id: bigint, degree: int]

paragraphs.text:
%sql
select degree, count(*) as paperCount from inDegrees group by degree order by paperCount

val outDegrees = graph.outDegrees.map({ case (id, count) => IdDegree(id, count)}).toDF.cache

outDegrees.registerTempTable("outDegrees")

%sql
select degree, count(*) as paperCount from outDegrees group by degree order by paperCount

case class NodeConnectedComponent(id: Long, cc: Long)
val ccGraph = graph.connectedComponents.cache
ccGraph.vertices.map({case(id, cc) => NodeConnectedComponent(id, cc)}).toDF.registerTempTable("cc")

%sql
select cc, count(*) nodeCount from cc group by cc having nodeCount > 5 order by nodeCount

val connectedGraph = ccGraph.subgraph(vpred = (_, cc) => cc == 1001)

connectedGraph.vertices.count

case class RankedPaper(id: Long, score: Double, title: String, authors: String, year: Int)
ppGraph.vertices.join(vertices)
    .map({case (id, (score, Paper(_, year, title, authors))) => RankedPaper(id, score, title, authors, year)})
    .toDF.registerTempTable("rankedPapers")

%sql
select id, score, title, authors, year from rankedPapers order by score desc limit 100
